snippet.title: Renowned Explorers Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Start your adventure now! (PC, Mac, Linux)
www.RenownedExplorers.com / http://store.steampowered.com/app/296970
http://www.gog.com/game/renowned_explorers

Renowned Explorers is a strategy adventure game set in a fictitious 19th century world, the Age of Discovery. 

Noteworthy are the original attitude-based gameplay and procedurally generated expeditions...

Become renowned for your treasures and reputation and start your adventure now!
